BEGIN_PGML

It's given that [` 1 \text{ gram} = 1000 \text{ milligrams} `]. Do the following unit conversions.

a. [`` [$g1] \text{ grams} = ``] [__________]{$mg1} [`` \text{ milligrams} ``]

a. [`` [$mg2] \text{ milligrams} = ``] [__________]{$g2} [`` \text{ grams} ``]

END_PGML


